// Title: Access to Network Shares
// Description: Detects when users access network shares which may indicate data collection from shared resources.
// Data Source: SecurityEvent
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0009 - Collection
//   Technique: T1039 - Data from Network Shared Drive
// Severity: High

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 5140
| project TimeGenerated, Account, Computer, ShareName, IpAddress
| order by TimeGenerated desc